parameters:
\SE[6]Oh my... There seems to be a rather dangerous guest here...
\SE[3]It might be a bit difficult to pick flowers together...

There are no 'defeat events' in this game. Feel free to beat them
up without hesitation.

\SE[19]Eei...! This is also for Lunaroa! \SE[17]I'm sorry, but
please let me handle this...!
\SE[17]\SM[nod]Hmm... I feel a bit guilty for some reason.

.........\SE[1]Well! It's survival of the fittest, right? Now,
the flowers I'm looking for should be around here...
\SE[22]Oh, I'm glad! I found it. Well then, let's get started...

\SE[22]\SM[jump]I did it! Oh my... I've really created something
amazing...
\i[182] The Suzuran hair ornament is complete!

\SE[0]It took longer than I thought. Maybe when I get home, I'll
show it to my mom too.
Do you want to move to the entrance of the back mountain?\!
\SE[0]Walking is good for your health, you know.
